nything that saves time can benefit accessibility.  Can you suggest important reasons while resumption of a download  benefits accessibility?    Thanks Jamal!     - Ian    --   Ian Jacobs (jacobs@w3.org)   http://www.w3.org/People/Jacobs  Tel/Fax:                     +1 212 684-1814  Cell:                        +1 917 450-8783        

