ill propose text.       CHECKPOINT 6.6       JT: Should we have somewhere a checkpoint stating that          the transformation should favor accessibility?       CMN: This is tricky since close to implementation level.       JT: Only area critical for access - human knows more.         (Same as previous checkpoint).       CMN: I would be wary of changing.       ACTION Jutta: Clarify proposal. CMN suggests talking     to Harvey Bingham (who sent proposal about time of     last IG review).        

