ne any external link checking on this document;      I will before going to last call.        [1] http://www.w3.org/WAI/UA/WD-UAAG10-20001021/  [2] http://www.w3.org/WAI/UA/WD-UAAG10-TECH-20001021/  [3] http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/w3c-wai-ua/2000OctDec/0083.html  [4] http://www.w3.org/WAI/UA/wai-ua-wd-changes.html  --   Ian Jacobs (jacobs@w3.org)   http://www.w3.org/People/Jacobs  Tel:                         +1 831 457-2842  Cell:                        +1 917 450-8783        

